text:
Mamimi～
Your hairstyle today is really cute～

If you react so enthusiastically
It's just going to make it harder to change my hairstyle.

Fufu, indeed. Such a big reaction might
just make her feel embarrassed.

Wha...!?
I just feel really happy whenever I get complemented though...

Okay then, the next time you change your hairstyle Kogane,
I'll be sure to give a you huge reaction...

Oh! Then when that time comes, we'll get to see an amaaazing reaction
that we normally wouldn't get to see from Mamimi, right?

Ugh, somewhow it seems like it's getting.
to where I can't get away with doing anything
